        </li>
        <li>
            Generate a multiplication table of <a asp-controller="Multiply" asp-action="AbruptTimeout" asp-route-count="5000" asp-route-timeout="5000"><strong>5000</strong> primes in <strong>5 seconds</strong> or die trying</a> <span class="text-info">(HTTP 400)</span>
        </li>
    </ul>
